title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Jul 1 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Jul 1 2022
description:
Biden's America is historically weak. C&B's pro tips for your 4th of July cookout. Food inflation. Clay and Buck talk ice cream flavors. Poll shows 79% of America doesn't want Biden to run again, but if 2024 is a referendum on Trump, he could be reelected. Buck's big tip for your BBQ: bacon. Jesse Kelly burger vs. Shake Shack. C&B take calls to wrap up the week.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
